Wow, an epic gameplay and stream ever :_るんるん: :_ちょうちょ:

So, this is another road at "Undertale"... I understood why that game became popular at their time (2015) and now recovered popularity.
Rushia-daitenshi was Immersed into game characters, really she's an innate talent: singer, actress (Also seiyuu)... And dancer if counting her few 3D live events. :_ハート:

A great encore for this gameplay, but Supaachaato Orei Time would wait until a next delivery.

Postscript: The BGM at intro is another of candidates to be an alternate Opening for "Hana ni hanasaku kimitachi e", "Be Happy" or "Summer Triangle"

Video Opening has no logo (Prototype version)
